etomica.virial.overlap

Class DataProcessorVirialOverlap

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.data.DataProcessor
      • etomica.virial.overlap.DataProcessorVirialOverlap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataPipe, IDataSink, AlphaSource

    public class DataProcessorVirialOverlap
extends DataProcessor
implements AlphaSource
    DataProcessor which takes in values for v/pi and pi2/pi (from MeterVirial) and calculates the overlap values for various values of alpha. This class can also act as an "AlphaSource"

        public void setBennetParam(double aCenter,

        Parameters:
